dct_description_sm: Relief partially shown by approximate contours and spot heights. "Vertical datum mean sea level." Map shows populated areas, shantytowns, roads, cemeteries, and notable features. Includes indexes of numbered features and streets, and glossary Includes location map, and boundary index. "Map information as of 1993." "Printed by DMAHTC 7-93." "NSN 7643014033629." "NIMA ref. no. Y921XMUQDISHO1." "Caution: This product may not conform to the horizontal accuracy requirements.
